.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab49617089bae06c18c6dbf325d20e29e5cbd703","tid":2047659,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e06c785e91e13227239f9ba5b00e1ced29f85aae","tid":2047659,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"混球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"改個咁既名<br />\n除左做警察都冇咩得好做"},{"pid":"eef68405e48ae522c75001c73ed1f10d3f8e77a7","tid":2047659,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:51:15.000Z","msg":"但可以接受警員做警察<br />\n下次繼續「警員誠實可靠」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7adcd2f1e9a6e30cdfddfd2600ca830cb74ac2a","tid":2047659,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"由呢單野可以得出結論：監於警察都有吹水唔抹嘴既癖好，辨方大律師日後應該重點質疑警察既口供矛盾，脫罪既機率會高好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外所有被捕手足如受到暴力對待，都應該大叫，因為片段好大機會呈堂時有用"},{"pid":"7f325be36b7731d2934c5c6afd30ac611aec6ff2","tid":2047659,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e06c785e91e13227239f9ba5b00e1ced29f85aae","tid":2047659,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"混球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"唔係咁寫咩？"},{"pid":"1085737e72014daab0dff4f7c76b7c2b450383c7","tid":2047659,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c853e47c028d43b0b46d1c504a2453d9a0e1f2ee","tid":2047659,"u